# 浏览器公开配置；不得在 VITE_* 变量中存放数据库、模型或身份凭证。
# OAuth public client ID is not a secret; it must match the Authorization Server registration for the active redirect URI.
# OAuth public client ID is not a secret. Copy this file to apps/web/.env for local Web development.
# The value must be registered by the Authorization Server for the exact redirect URI:
# - local development: http://localhost:5173/oauth/callback
# - production/preview: https://<canonical-web-origin>/oauth/callback
# Replace this controlled local example if your team issued a different public Web client ID.
VITE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=aiws-web-local

# 可选的前端诊断批量上传；三项均省略时不会发送任何诊断网络请求。
# host 和 port 必须同时配置；协议省略时默认为 HTTPS。
# HTTP 只接受 localhost 或 127.0.0.1 的本地开发接收器；公网接收器必须 HTTPS。
# VITE_DIAGNOSTICS_PROTOCOL=https
# VITE_DIAGNOSTICS_HOSTNAME=diagnostics.example.com
# VITE_DIAGNOSTICS_PORT=443
